data.hoverText: 可与单数或复数动词连用的可数名词

data.enText: an organized group of criminals

data.chText: 犯罪集团成员和毒品贩子
data.enText: criminal gang members and drug dealers
a gang of pickpockets

data.chText: 这起抢劫是一个四人团伙所为。
data.enText: A four-man gang carried out the robbery.

data.chText: 一帮，一群，一伙（闹事、斗殴的年轻人）
data.enText: a group of young people who spend a lot of time together and often cause trouble or fight against other groups
a gang of youths
a street gang

data.chText: 一伙（经常聚在一起的朋友）
data.enText: a group of friends who meet regularly
The whole gang will be there.

data.chText: 一队，一组（一起干活的工人、囚犯等）
data.enText: an organized group of workers or prisoners doing work together
gang together
to join together in a group in order to have more power or strength
gang up (on/against sb)

data.chText: 结伙，联合起来，拉帮结派（伤害、恐吓或反对某人）
data.enText: to join together in a group to hurt, frighten or oppose sb

data.chText: 在学校读书时那些大男孩联合起来欺负他，辱骂他。
data.enText: At school the older boys ganged up on him and called him names.

tr: tool consisting of a combination of implements arranged to work together

example: police tried to break up the gang
he still hangs out with the same crowd

value.def: A gang is a group of people, especially young people, who go around together and often deliberately cause trouble.

example.ex: During the fight with a rival gang he lashed out with his flick knife...
example.tran: 在与敌对帮派的打斗中，他挥舞着弹簧折刀一通猛刺。

example.ex: Gang members were behind a lot of the violence...
example.tran: 很多暴力事件是流氓团伙成员暗中策划的。

example.ex: He was attacked by a gang of youths.
example.tran: 他遭到一帮小混混的袭击。

value.tran: 一帮，一伙（尤指滋事的年轻人）

value.def: A gang is a group of criminals who work together to commit crimes.

example.ex: Police were hunting for a gang who had allegedly stolen fifty-five cars.
example.tran: 警方正在追捕一个被控盗窃了55辆汽车的犯罪团伙。

value.def: The gang is a group of friends who frequently meet.

example.ex: Come on over, we've got lots of the old gang here.
example.tran: 过来吧，好多老朋友都在这儿。

value.def: A gang is a group of workers who do physical work together.
value.tran: 一群，一队，一组（一起干体力活的人）
